name: Spooky
description: When the spooks have a midnight jamboree They break it up with fiendish glee The ghosts are bad but the one that’s cursed is skeleton dan mummy he’s the worst!That’s right, he’s a fright on Halloween night!When he goes a joggin’ ‘cross the land Holding his noggin in his hand/Demons take one look and groan And they hit the road to parts unknown/Beware, take care he rides alone!
